{"type":"message","id":"2bd748f4","parentId":"5057cd13","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:29:34.349Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7tdjom7oquti_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 3153\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='research/cfi_compression_experiment.md' new_len=1423\n[mutation proposed] research/cfi_compression_experiment.md\n[master 039284c] pulse: 2026-03-24 122916\n 6 files changed, 198 insertions(+), 70 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 122916.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 122916.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 122814.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 122916 - The CFI analysis revealed that 94.3% of frequency-invariants are either noise (CFI=0) or low-signal (CFI<0.7). A CFI-weighted compression experiment is needed to validate whether filtering by CFI threshold improves next-pulse prediction over frequency-only baseline.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"faint-wharf","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 3153\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='research/cfi_compression_experiment.md' new_len=1423\n[mutation proposed] research/cfi_compression_experiment.md\n[master 039284c] pulse: 2026-03-24 122916\n 6 files changed, 198 insertions(+), 70 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 122916.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 122916.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 122814.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 122916 - The CFI analysis revealed that 94.3% of frequency-invariants are either noise (CFI=0) or low-signal (CFI<0.7). A CFI-weighted compression experiment is needed to validate whether filtering by CFI threshold improves next-pulse prediction over frequency-only baseline.\n","name":"powershell C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\san